'''These are the instructions for installing LyXBlogger on your machine.
Open a shell. (cmd on Windows)
Navigate to the same directory where this file is located.

To install normally (includes wordpresslib and elyxer):
  python setup.py install

To install without installing elyxer (still includeds wordpresslib)
  python setup-no-elyxer.py install

LyXBlogger is now installed as a module on your system. You invoke it 
by calling 
  python -m lyxblogger input_file.(x)html

